# ControlFlow Core

This is a prompt/governance/eval repository, not a runtime application.
Canonical multi-agent policies, roster, and tiers are governed by `.github/copilot-instructions.md` and `plans/project-context.md`.
Cursor workflow: skills in `.cursor/skills/controlflow-*/`, subagents in `.cursor/agents/controlflow-*.md`, plugin package `plugins/controlflow-cursor/`.
Entry: follow skill `controlflow-strict-workflow` for non-trivial tasks.
Use `Task(subagent_type=...)` for delegation when available; see `docs/agent-engineering/CURSOR-SUPPORT.md` for fallback.
Cursor cannot execute VS Code-only semantics (`agent/runSubagent`, `@Planner` UI). Do not claim otherwise.
`AGENTS.md` is compatibility context only, not the primary Cursor artifact.
All changes must pass: `cd evals && npm test`.
